title: ‘PLOT TWIST!’ Greg Gutfeld presents a ‘what if’ about whistleblower’s identity (can Joe Biden confirm?)
text:
As Twitchy told you Tuesday evening, the Trump administration said it will release both a transcript of Trump’s call with Ukraine’s president and the whistleblower complaint this week. For now, speculation is running rampant, but Greg Gutfeld posed a “what if” for the ages:

what if the whistleblower is corn pop — GregGutfeld (@greggutfeld) September 25, 2019

Ha! Hey, at this point anything is possible.

LMFAO. ONE LINER OF THE YEAR! https://t.co/9j8BtYdHWn — Brad Loflin (@BradL6567) September 25, 2019

Corn Pop and T-Bone would make for an entertaining Netflix series. https://t.co/FHUXhJQkQp — Sam Valley (@SamValley) September 25, 2019

They sure would.
